<br>
Scenario : Your pet is attacking another player. You cast Annul. Pet poofs.<br>
<br>
This happens every single time in Pvp.<br>
<br>
I've been having to live with this for a long time now. I send in my pet, start casting Annul. Just before Annul lands I have to /pet back off, then /pet attack again once the annul lands. It's very annoying, and I've sort of gotten used to it.<br>
